text:
Booze-fueled Ben Affleck has reached his boiling point with estranged wife Jennifer Garner! RadarOnline.com has learned exclusively a full-scale brawl between the two broke out in a Los Angeles park after their son Samuel’s basketball game.

Shocking photos show the separated stars erupting in a fiery argument on Feb. 4 over Gerner’s frustrations with Affleck’s wild lifestyle! “Jen’s furious with Ben’s infantile behavior and demanded he quit boozing and biking,” an insider told RadarOnline.com. Click through to see photos of the duo's nasty basket-brawl!
